00:21:18,440 --> 00:21:24,290
Even more so when Father owes them a life. I want to use this redeem ourselves.

250
00:21:24,290 --> 00:21:26,350
Brother Shao Tian knows about management.

251
00:21:26,350 --> 00:21:30,410
In my opinion, no one is more suitable than him to run Rong Da.

252
00:21:33,190 --> 00:21:36,520
How did Zhou Shao Tian charm you?

253
00:21:36,520 --> 00:21:39,290
When he was doing well, you didn't want to be with him.

254
00:21:39,290 --> 00:21:42,000
Not that he's broke and not worth anything,

255
00:21:42,000 --> 00:21:45,900
you still sympathize with him and you even want to help him.

256
00:21:46,790 --> 00:21:49,140
Do you want to marry him?

257
00:21:50,120 --> 00:21:54,620
After having gone through so many events, it's impossible for the both of us.

258
00:21:55,810 --> 00:21:58,960
Cai Yun. Don't just stand here and say nothing.

259
00:21:58,960 --> 00:22:01,150
Rong Da belongs to the Wu family.

260
00:22:01,150 --> 00:22:03,320
What are your views?

261
00:22:03,320 --> 00:22:05,590
Sister is right. I will listen to her.

262
00:22:05,590 --> 00:22:07,440
You!

263
00:22:10,010 --> 00:22:14,220
I don't care. Even if the both of you can't manage the company,

264
00:22:14,220 --> 00:22:15,850
we can still sell Rong Da.

265
00:22:15,850 --> 00:22:18,080
Why should we give it to Zhou Shao Tian?

266
00:22:18,080 --> 00:22:21,330
Mom. We are already very fortunate to have our home.

267
00:22:21,330 --> 00:22:25,210
Even so, father snatched Ling Long away from the Jiang family.

268
00:22:25,210 --> 00:22:27,450
I feel that Sister is right in doing this.

269
00:22:27,450 --> 00:22:30,350
Just give in to Sister.

270
00:22:32,680 --> 00:22:34,600
- Mom. <br>- Stepmom.

271
00:23:16,850 --> 00:23:19,110
Aunt.

272
00:23:20,480 --> 00:23:22,300
Brother Shao Tian.

273
00:23:22,300 --> 00:23:26,080
Cai Hong, you are here.

274
00:23:26,940 --> 00:23:28,150
- Aunt. <br>- Miss Wu.

275
00:23:28,150 --> 00:23:32,540
- What are you doing? Get up. <br>- Thank you.

276
00:23:32,540 --> 00:23:35,850
Shao Tian and I should publish a notice of thanks.

277
00:23:35,850 --> 00:23:38,320
Thank you for your kindness in saving him.

278
00:23:38,320 --> 00:23:42,170
Thank you for signing an amicable settlement with him and giving him his freedom.

279
00:23:42,170 --> 00:23:46,810
I will never be able to repay your kindness in this lifetime.

280
00:23:46,810 --> 00:23:48,910
Aunt, get up first.

281
00:23:48,910 --> 00:23:50,990
Get up first and we will talk.

282
00:23:52,030 --> 00:23:56,310
When my family was in trouble, he has helped us a lot.

283
00:23:56,310 --> 00:23:59,990
So, this is what I should do.

284
00:24:03,030 --> 00:24:08,690
Cai Hong. Don't worry. I will find of a way to find your father's killer.

285
00:24:08,690 --> 00:24:12,160
I will continue to investigate this.

286
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:17,900
But I'm here today to discuss something else with Brother Shao Tian.

287
00:24:18,610 --> 00:24:20,460
Speak.

288
00:24:22,630 --> 00:24:27,970
I have decided to let you manage Rong Da.

289
00:24:27,970 --> 00:24:33,650
Miss Wu. We don't deserve this. You are already being extremely kind to forgive Shao Tian.

290
00:24:33,650 --> 00:24:38,310
- With Rong Da, we cannot accept it. <br>- Cai Hong, did you take into consideration that

291
00:24:38,310 --> 00:24:41,690
