292
00:24:41,690 --> 00:24:46,730
Brother Shao Tian. I made this decision after carefully considering this.

293
00:24:46,730 --> 00:24:49,840
Rong Da is an exquisite and profitable company.

294
00:24:49,840 --> 00:24:51,590
It's also part of Ling Long.

295
00:24:51,590 --> 00:24:53,440
It's also my father's business.

296
00:24:53,440 --> 00:24:57,530
You should know that Cai Yun and I doesn't know anything about management.

297
00:24:57,530 --> 00:25:00,290
It will only go bankrupt in our hands.

298
00:25:00,290 --> 00:25:04,090
Why don't we hand it over to someone who's experienced to manage it?

299
00:25:04,090 --> 00:25:08,980
I believe that Rong Da will do well under your management.

300
00:25:09,800 --> 00:25:11,520
Huzhou is such a big place.

301
00:25:11,520 --> 00:25:15,020
I'm not the only know who knows about the dyeing industry.

302
00:25:17,760 --> 00:25:22,030
But our Wu family only trusts you.

303
00:25:24,170 --> 00:25:28,410
Your father's death was also caused by my father.

304
00:25:28,410 --> 00:25:31,470
I hope that I can use it to redeem my family.

305
00:25:31,470 --> 00:25:33,870
It's already in the past.

306
00:25:33,870 --> 00:25:36,220
We have already clear this up.

307
00:25:36,220 --> 00:25:37,760
Even more so,

308
00:25:37,760 --> 00:25:40,990
I also wronged the Wu family.

309
00:25:43,670 --> 00:25:44,910
That's because

310
00:25:44,910 --> 00:25:47,850
you feel apologetic towards my family and Lin Long.

311
00:25:47,850 --> 00:25:51,500
Thus, you should manage Rong Da well

312
00:25:51,500 --> 00:25:56,040
and manage my father's business well.

313
00:26:08,370 --> 00:26:12,380
Do you really want to me to manage Rong Da?

314
00:26:13,730 --> 00:26:14,980
Yes.

315
00:26:18,670 --> 00:26:21,860
Okay, I agree.

316
00:26:26,440 --> 00:26:31,910
This is the authorization paper. Brother Shao Tian is the General Manager of Rong Da.

317
00:26:42,490 --> 00:26:44,150
Also,

318
00:26:47,930 --> 00:26:49,990
this bracelet,

319
00:26:54,330 --> 00:26:56,770
I'm returning this to you.

320
00:27:03,300 --> 00:27:04,750
As of now,

321
00:27:05,890 --> 00:27:07,960
we don't owe each other anything else.

322
00:27:23,940 --> 00:27:25,780
Cai Hong.

323
00:27:27,580 --> 00:27:30,610
Is this the answer that you are giving me?

324
00:27:34,760 --> 00:27:37,070
I remember you told me that

325
00:27:38,570 --> 00:27:41,010
we can start anew.

326
00:27:48,760 --> 00:27:50,720
Sorry.

327
00:27:50,720 --> 00:27:53,530
You don't need to apologise to me.

328
00:27:53,530 --> 00:27:56,470
You really don't need to.

329
00:27:56,470 --> 00:27:58,880
This is fate.

330
00:27:58,880 --> 00:28:01,450
I can only hate fate.

331
00:28:01,450 --> 00:28:06,110
If I didn't have any grudges with your family, we wouldn't have come to this stage.

332
00:28:13,720 --> 00:28:15,460
Brother Shao Tian.

333
00:28:17,810 --> 00:28:20,720
This bad deed

334
00:28:20,720 --> 00:28:24,630
met with a wrong opponent.

335
00:28:24,630 --> 00:28:25,980
Thus,

336
00:28:27,390 --> 00:28:30,040
everything was doomed.

337
00:28:32,330 --> 00:28:37,070
As for happiness, it depends on the right time

338
00:28:39,050 --> 00:28:41,590
and the right person.

339
00:28:54,190 --> 00:28:56,180
It's Jiang Yu, right?

340
00:29:12,480 --> 00:29:19,030
Brother Shao Tian. You will meet a better woman than me.

341
00:29:49,530 --> 00:29:51,250
<i>Cai Hong.</i>

342
00:29:52,720 --> 00:29:55,460
<i>Whether you care or not,</i>

343
00:29:55,460 --> 00:29:57,990
<i>whether you respond or not,</i>

344
00:29:58,970 --> 00:30:03,570
<i>or whether you know or not,</i>

345
00:30:03,570 --> 00:30:05,870
<i>that in this world,</i>

346
00:30:05,870 --> 00:30:10,870
<i>there will always be someone watching over you.</i>

347
00:30:16,480 --> 00:30:19,010
<i>Beatiful and bright rainbow,</i>

348
00:30:19,010 --> 00:30:23,060
<i>appears only when the skies are no longer filled with rain.</i>

349
00:30:23,060 --> 00:30:25,900
<i>No matter how, we will never be able to catch it.</i>

350
00:30:29,760 --> 00:30:31,030
Brother.

351
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:35,630
- Fei Fei. <br>-I got good news.

352
00:30:35,630 --> 00:30:38,940
Wu Cai Hong gave Rong Da to Zhou Shao Tian.

353
00:30:44,280 --> 00:30:47,960
Looks like Wu Cai Hong loves Zhou Shao Tian very much.

354
00:30:47,960 --> 00:30:52,360
Brother Zhou Shao Tian did so many things. She didn't even teach him a lesson.

355
00:30:52,360 --> 00:30:55,330
That's because Wu Cai Hong is too kind.

356
00:30:55,330 --> 00:30:59,990
Good always prevails against evil. We can only hope it can also ever come the hatred.

357
00:31:01,600 --> 00:31:03,140
Brother.

358
00:31:03,140 --> 00:31:08,060
Then... do you still like Wu Cai Hong?

359
00:31:08,920 --> 00:31:10,530
Do you have any other matters?

360
00:31:10,530 --> 00:31:12,420
If no, I'm going to work.

361
00:31:13,690 --> 00:31:15,950
You are going to work now?

362
00:31:15,950 --> 00:31:21,360
When you were injured and stayed in the hospital, you still went out with Cai Hong with your wounds.

363
00:31:21,360 --> 00:31:25,490
I see you are quite bored recently.

364
00:31:25,490 --> 00:31:29,990
Brother, until when are you going to act like this?

365
00:31:31,490 --> 00:31:33,530
I already said many times.

366
00:31:33,530 --> 00:31:38,120
I did this to find out who the killer of Wu Hong Da is.

367
00:31:38,120 --> 00:31:40,350
Do you need to do this?

368
00:31:40,350 --> 00:31:43,210
It has already been proven that you are not the killer.

369
00:31:43,210 --> 00:31:47,010
Who the killer is, it doesn't concern us at all.

370
00:31:48,180 --> 00:31:51,300
You are trying to help Wu Cai Hong to find the killer.

371
00:31:51,300 --> 00:31:55,130
Frankly, you still want to be with her.

372
00:31:58,510 --> 00:32:00,790
Are you done talking?

373
00:32:13,080 --> 00:32:16,760
Miss, Director Chen is requesting to see you.

374
00:32:21,310 --> 00:32:23,270
Director Chen?

375
00:32:25,200 --> 00:32:27,190
Let him wait downstairs.

376
00:32:27,190 --> 00:32:28,570
Yes.

377
00:32:36,450 --> 00:32:39,520
- Miss Lu. <br>- Director Chen.

378
00:32:39,520 --> 00:32:42,700
I didn't notify you in advance. I hope that I didn't impose on you.

379
00:32:42,700 --> 00:32:45,010
Talking about this, you did.

380
00:32:45,010 --> 00:32:46,950
I have an appointment with the Military Governor.

381
00:32:46,950 --> 00:32:50,720
If you insist that I don't go, I don't have a choice then.

382
00:32:50,720 --> 00:32:52,560
Please sit.

383
00:32:52,560 --> 00:32:53,730
Okay.

384
00:32:58,030 --> 00:33:01,300
I wonder why you are here to see me.

385
00:33:01,300 --> 00:33:05,360
Miss Lu. I have a few questions to consult you.

386
00:33:05,360 --> 00:33:06,740
Please speak.

387
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:08,690
Regarding the previous owner, Wu Hong Da,

388
00:33:08,690 --> 00:33:11,070
do you still remember him, Miss Lu?

389
00:33:12,360 --> 00:33:14,080
Yes.

390
00:33:14,080 --> 00:33:17,800
We investigated and heard that before the incident happened to Wu Hong Da,

391
00:33:17,800 --> 00:33:19,900
you went to meet him.

392
00:33:19,900 --> 00:33:24,370
Yes. At that time, I wanted to set up a dyeing factory in Huzhou.

393
00:33:24,370 --> 00:33:26,570
Thus, I paid him a visit.

394
00:33:26,570 --> 00:33:29,470
The first time was with my father, when I wanted to get acquainted with him.

395
00:33:29,470 --> 00:33:32,630
And the second time was when I wanted to share something with Master Wu.

396
00:33:32,630 --> 00:33:36,850
What's wrong with this?

397
00:33:36,850 --> 00:33:41,740
Looks like Miss Lu is very interested in the secret formula.

398
00:33:42,480 --> 00:33:47,520
I do want the secret formula but within Huzhou,

399
00:33:47,520 --> 00:33:49,960
there are many others who want it too.

400
00:33:49,960 --> 00:33:54,790
Director Chen. Think about this. If Wu Hong Da didn't have the secret formula,

401
00:33:54,790 --> 00:33:57,690
first, I'm not short of money and contacts.

402
00:33:57,690 --> 00:34:00,570
Why would I want to share it with him?

403
00:34:00,570 --> 00:34:02,890
Then, on the day of Wu Hong Da's incident,

404
00:34:02,890 --> 00:34:04,410
did you see him?

405
00:34:04,410 --> 00:34:07,320
It was such a long time ago.,

406
00:34:07,320 --> 00:34:08,750
How could I remember it?

407
00:34:08,750 --> 00:34:11,740
Please try to remember.

408
00:34:15,320 --> 00:34:20,600
It seems like I was with a friend that day.

409
00:34:20,600 --> 00:34:25,450
Director Chen. Since you have the time, why don't you pay that friend of mine a visit?

410
00:34:25,450 --> 00:34:28,230
He should be able to testify.

411
00:34:28,230 --> 00:34:33,290
Listening to you, are you suspecting me?

412
00:34:33,290 --> 00:34:34,750
Of course not.

413
00:34:34,750 --> 00:34:38,230
We rely on evidence in our line of work.

414
00:34:38,230 --> 00:34:42,040
I just want to clear every detail of this case.

415
00:34:42,040 --> 00:34:46,370
By the way, Miss Lu, I would still like to ask you a question.

416
00:34:46,370 --> 00:34:50,090
Wu Hong Da's staff, Old Cai, was kidnapped a few days ago.

417
00:34:50,090 --> 00:34:52,300
It wasn't easy for us to save him.

418
00:34:52,300 --> 00:34:56,330
In the end, he told me that the person who kidnapped him was a young woman.

419
00:34:56,330 --> 00:34:57,650
She also kept asking about

420
00:34:57,650 --> 00:35:00,140
- the secret formula... <br>- Director Chen.

421
00:35:00,140 --> 00:35:02,440
In Huzhou,

422
00:35:02,440 --> 00:35:04,470
there are many young women.

423
00:35:04,470 --> 00:35:07,040
If you came to question me based on a groundless rumour,

424
00:35:07,040 --> 00:35:09,760
I feel it is a little bit inappropriate.

425
00:35:09,760 --> 00:35:13,700
It was Zhou Shao Tian's man, Ma Li who told us that

426
00:35:13,700 --> 00:35:16,520
he told you that the secret formula was with Old Cai's wife.

427
00:35:16,520 --> 00:35:19,320
Yes. Ma Li did tell me.

428
00:35:19,320 --> 00:35:22,890
I also used his tip to find Old Cai's wife

429
00:35:22,890 --> 00:35:27,090
but Director Chen, I looked for his wife to buy the secret formula.

430
00:35:27,090 --> 00:35:29,040
I didn't do anything else.

431
00:35:29,040 --> 00:35:34,530
If this is the case, I can also prove that Jiang Yu went to find Old Cai's wife for the secret formula too.

432
00:35:34,530 --> 00:35:36,780
Furthermore, the secret formula belongs to the Jiang family in the first place.

433
00:35:36,780 --> 00:35:41,000
He would want the secret formula more than I do.

434
00:35:41,000 --> 00:35:43,100
Is this how you conduct your case?

435
00:35:43,100 --> 00:35:46,680
Director Chen. You said that you are not suspecting me

436
00:35:46,680 --> 00:35:50,930
but to me it seems like you are investigating me undercover.

437
00:35:50,930 --> 00:35:54,920
Sorry. I have an appointment with the Military Governor.

438
00:35:54,920 --> 00:35:57,050
I won't be seeing you out.

439
00:36:04,530 --> 00:36:11,030
Miss Lu. I'm only here today on official matters. If I have offended you, please accept my apologies.

440
00:36:11,990 --> 00:36:17,700
Director Chen. I hope that you find concrete evidence first before you return here with official matters.

441
00:36:17,700 --> 00:36:20,890
I'm not this patient all the time.

442
00:36:22,060 --> 00:36:24,990
Uncle Lai, see the guest out.

443
00:36:26,790 --> 00:36:29,550
This way, please.

444
00:36:51,400 --> 00:36:53,880
Sister, what are you doing?

445
00:36:53,880 --> 00:36:56,920
I am packing a milled powder.

446
00:36:56,920 --> 00:36:59,920
- Are you having a fever? <br>- It's not for me.

447
00:36:59,920 --> 00:37:01,650
Is it Brother Shao Tian then?

448
00:37:01,650 --> 00:37:03,210
No.

449
00:37:07,050 --> 00:37:09,490
Sister, where are you going?

450
00:37:09,490 --> 00:37:14,410
To the police station to check if there is any progress in the case. Be good and wait here for me.

451
00:37:14,410 --> 00:37:16,540
Police station?

452
00:37:17,670 --> 00:37:21,070
If she's not going with Brother Shao Tian,

453
00:37:21,070 --> 00:37:23,640
she must be going with Jiang Yu.

454
00:37:23,640 --> 00:37:24,510
Mr Jiang.

455
00:37:24,510 --> 00:37:26,590
Uncle Lai. Prepare the rickshaw.

456
00:37:26,590 --> 00:37:28,450
I'm going to see the Military Governor.

457
00:37:28,450 --> 00:37:29,980
Miss.

458
00:37:38,320 --> 00:37:41,610
Military Governor. What are you here?

459
00:37:41,610 --> 00:37:44,020
Did you come to pick me up?

460
00:38:02,490 --> 00:38:06,810
Who is so brave to make you so angry?

461
00:38:06,810 --> 00:38:11,330
Chief Police Li just phoned me.

462
00:38:11,330 --> 00:38:14,330
He said that Director Chen will be visiting you to have a talk.

463
00:38:14,330 --> 00:38:19,030
I believe you already met Superintendent Chen.

464
00:38:20,330 --> 00:38:23,120
I thought what could happen. It's just this small matter.

465
00:38:23,120 --> 00:38:25,450
You are unhappy.

466
00:38:25,450 --> 00:38:27,070
Is that so?

467
00:38:30,310 --> 00:38:32,770
Human life is such a trivial issue, right?

468
00:38:32,770 --> 00:38:36,010
Yet what else could be bigger than this?

469
00:38:39,620 --> 00:38:41,190
Military Governor.

470
00:38:42,310 --> 00:38:44,910
I have been framed.

471
00:38:51,430 --> 00:38:54,220
I raised flowers to look at them.

472
00:38:54,220 --> 00:38:57,170
I raised a dog out of boredom.

473
00:38:57,170 --> 00:39:00,410
I raised you so that you can live well.

474
00:39:00,410 --> 00:39:03,300
It's to make me happy

475
00:39:03,300 --> 00:39:05,950
and not for you to give me trouble!

476
00:39:08,190 --> 00:39:11,410
Military Governor. I was framed. I didn't do anything.

477
00:39:11,410 --> 00:39:16,100
Don't be so anxious to explain yourself. I am a warlord.

478
00:39:16,100 --> 00:39:19,300
Even dogs hide from me.

479
00:39:22,960 --> 00:39:26,010
I would also never let anyone take advantage of me.

480
00:39:26,970 --> 00:39:32,240
Moreover, you are better than a dog. At least you can talk.

481
00:39:32,240 --> 00:39:34,760
But mark this.

482
00:39:34,760 --> 00:39:38,990
If you give me any trouble and make me unhappy,

483
00:39:38,990 --> 00:39:41,830
I will strangle you to death.

484
00:39:42,390 --> 00:39:45,210
I understand. I won't give you any trouble.

485
00:39:45,210 --> 00:39:47,840
I definitely won't give you any trouble.

486
00:39:47,840 --> 00:39:52,290
I don't care whether you really did it or not.

487
00:39:52,290 --> 00:39:54,110
Don't ever do it again.

488
00:39:55,920 --> 00:39:57,290
I understand.

489
00:39:57,290 --> 00:40:02,060
In the future, I will only make you happy and won't give you any trouble.

490
00:40:04,830 --> 00:40:09,170
Don't be sad. I already talked to Chief Police Li.

491
00:40:09,170 --> 00:40:13,960
If they don't have any real evidence, they won't dare to disturb you again.

492
00:40:19,720 --> 00:40:24,170
I know that you still dote on me.

493
00:40:24,170 --> 00:40:26,490
You said that

494
00:40:26,490 --> 00:40:29,780
I'm better than a dog.

495
00:40:29,780 --> 00:40:33,610
I will be better than a dog.

496
00:40:33,610 --> 00:40:36,370
Do you know that?

497
00:40:36,370 --> 00:40:39,120
Will I really know that?

498
00:40:39,120 --> 00:40:40,870
Military Governor.

499
00:40:46,250 --> 00:40:47,900
Military Governor.

