00:40:57,290 --> 00:41:00,170
I made this drug accordingly to the Chinese medicine' recipe.

501
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:02,720
It will help the injuries to heal faster.

502
00:41:02,720 --> 00:41:05,140
You can try this.

